Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.97,0:00:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷疑近衛史菜就是頂之座  赫卡特的夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.99,0:00:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在來襲的徒面前作了一個極限賭博
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於面臨著危機也一動不動的史菜  夏娜終於打消了疑慮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  看著接近著悠二的史菜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.97,0:00:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜的心中再次出現了新的動盪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近衛同學  最近一段時間我每天早上都會來接你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什麼煩惱的話  請儘管說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要客氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.74,0:02:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近衛  你又出麻煩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來需要一個人時刻看顧著你才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.85,0:02:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是最為合適的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近衛  你坐到池的旁邊去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了  還不快點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼非得是悠二不可
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒辦法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她好像有點黏著我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.09,0:03:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她習慣這裡的生活前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得在各方面都好好幫助她才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  坂井君  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  近衛同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是專程在這裡等我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為明明我也是要看顧近衛同學的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻把接送近衛同學的工作都交給坂井君你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是跟你說過了不用在意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為吉田同學你家剛好是相反的方向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上學放學就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.16,0:03:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在女孩子的一些問題方面就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點走上課會遲到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼體育課會叫我們打掃游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  總比對著書桌好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近衛同學  不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在偷什麼懶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  這樣拿著刷子  感覺像往前推
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  緒方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會等你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回敬你  可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敢來就來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊來啊  我在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.06,0:05:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:05:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天吃的也是干鰹魚的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就那麼喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  干鰹魚的飯糰很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.56,0:06:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井你可真幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然可以吃兩個便當
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  近衛同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是一美為了坂井君才做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必在意  沒有關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就一點點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  這個你也想…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我已經給悠二你了  隨你喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  吉田同學  明天再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是這樣目送著他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池君…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也跟過去如何呢  本來你就負責看顧她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看顧她…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼連吉田一美也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時只有我跟悠二兩個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那家店是新開的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的啊  明天開張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣呢  明天放學的時候  也叫上池大家一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大碗天國…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  近衛史菜不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近衛同學  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便亂跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家可都是為了陪你才這樣做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這方面你注意一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.83,0:08:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:08:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著那麼生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要到這種地方來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說  到頭來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個轉學生也沒有任何的異常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  她大概是我們學校裡最不會惹是生非的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外界宿那邊應該已經作出回應了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還沒有任何化裝舞會重新開始活動了的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是無中生有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把赫卡特單獨一人送往火霧戰士身邊這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是貝魯佩爾也不可能會做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  既然零時迷子帶著戒禁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能明白你想要慎重的心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  「外界宿」到底指的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們火霧戰士進行情報交換的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互助設施
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是討厭被淋濕的火霧戰士們會聚集的極少數的地方之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這種地方那麼悠閒地待著真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小丫頭與密斯提斯的小弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在估計鍛煉正進展得火熱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾幾次沒有問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你已經有點認同悠二了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少之又少
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼今天  那裡以及這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就都當作是歡樂時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井那傢伙  竟以火霧戰士為對手在進行著訓練嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏  夏娜  是不是比以前更猛烈了點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說廢話了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…  我會如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井悠二  要從力量的脈動去感知動作的始動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.81,0:11:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.66,0:12:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的感知能力非常敏銳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體內還蘊藏著能夠匹敵紅世之王的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據你日後的成長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許還能發現一條與普通的火炬  普通的密斯提斯都不同的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的道路？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  只有你才能夠前進的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二一定能夠變強的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要努力的話一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.22,0:12:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你不被無關緊要的事所迷惑的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大碗天國
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這家店了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:13:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是少見啊  佐藤和田中居然也來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到大碗以後哪還坐得住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大碗咖哩久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大碗豬排飯久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.69,0:13:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大碗拉麵久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大碗又一丁拉麵久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠資格做我的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井  決一勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不大明白  但我不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜  真打算一個人吃完它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們才是  三個人吃的話不就沒意義了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.17,0:13:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說已經算很多的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個  都不要太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上  都給我放馬過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在幹什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  平手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  近衛同學她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近衛同學不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  她不在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來還以為會在洗手間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  先去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼悠二必須去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於為什麼  畢竟我是照顧她的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不是學校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在是回家的路上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也約好送她回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前已經警告過近衛史菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便亂跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是不作聲就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還有必要去找她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在生什麼氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.67,0:15:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是在生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:16:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的傢伙  別管就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做到那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都知道她不是徒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這事無關
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我沒看好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別太在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也分頭去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.55,0:16:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近衛同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.71,0:17:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是從野貓那裡救下來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是把紅蘿蔔洗乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我是在嫉妒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的心情  真討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.45,0:19:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天晚上開始  我將成為你的陪練
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們好像很喜歡那個新窩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜同學不在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上的鍛煉也沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.83,0:20:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.46,0:21:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.07,0:21:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.28,0:21:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.41,0:21:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同學到圖書委員會去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏娜  到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.33,0:23:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因史菜的事情而感情無法平靜的夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.49,0:23:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因夏娜的言行而困惑的威爾艾米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.79,0:23:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因一點小爭執引起了夏娜的怒火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.43,0:23:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無可奈何的威爾艾米娜  得到了悠二的母親千草的建議
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.55,0:24:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  灼眼的夏娜第二季
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.15,0:24:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家庭的餐桌
